Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那之后战况如何 哈库莱特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以扬陆城降落地点为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成了对维多利亚湖周边的镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由多个轨道骑士所组成的共同战线…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此力量产生恐惧的恐怕不仅仅是地球联合军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过此次的成果 我相信所有人都应该会明白领导者的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们根本就没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有Aldnoah力量却仍会在地球上陷入苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aldnoah吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎赫巴姆伯爵曾对建立在Aldnoah启动权上的阶级社会感到忧虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.89,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甚至认为移民火星一事本身就是个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为拥有那种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人类了移民火星 开始了这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是亚瑟拉姆公主 还是雷姆蕾娜公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都是Aldnoah的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被此力量吞噬的日子已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要将此次战斗中获得的领土作为基石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终将领土扩大到整个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 将丰富的资源和Aldnoah的力量相结合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来创造属于我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维修的状况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太乐观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电缆被烧坏了 要花费不少时间进行更换
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏在这种时候开始作战吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deucalion无法行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能使用登陆艇将重甲骑兵送往前线呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的两个小队从北面进攻敌人的扬陆城 扰乱敌方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此掩护从西南方向攻过来的强袭部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“游击部队”就是说着好听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们还是被当成弃子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许司令部那边有什么胜算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们所想的胜算也把我们包含在内了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下 我们得为自己多做一下打算了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 界冢弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些火星人 就不能凭借你那聪明才智将他们搞定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想很难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将高电压作为武器的 Elektris
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透明化的 Skandia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两台都不好对付
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于Ortygia的分身能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所持有的数据还太少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷击 分身以及隐身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是千叶真一的电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过观测我目前所了解的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ortygia一定会由一台机体分成二台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不会一次分成三台以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2台所出现的距离是半径30米以内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对方如何分身 敌人所搭乘的本体只有一台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它的都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么只有找出本体将它打倒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有标记出分身之前的那架机体进行追击了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于Skandia 只要使用烟幕弹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以通过烟雾的流向来断定其位置所在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷击那架呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么对应方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果吃上那家伙一击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是电子回路还是促动器都会一击爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:33.60,ruby,NTP,150,0,0,,actuator
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用绝缘体如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不导电的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？你傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是小学生么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊？我哪里说错了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气已经是绝缘体了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法对抗强大到足以打穿了多层绝缘的高压电
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加麻烦的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些辣手的敌人在联合作战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单独一架机体就够难对付的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许…有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要用那只眼睛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用为我担心 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在运行着进化代码
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.72,ruby,NTP,330,0,0,,mutation code
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间越长 它会越来越优化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演算能力和以前相比也提升了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡姆 可以帮我换一下装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想换啥尽管说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用在宇宙所使用的那套装备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷姆蕾娜公主 侵略地球一事正在顺利进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 不负所望呢 斯雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 可以请您表彰一下获得战功的轨道骑士们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我”来说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 亚瑟拉姆公主表彰他们的功绩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有更多的轨道骑士站到我们这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:06:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我们”？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外问一下 斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇姐的病情如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听报告说 她依然危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在只有相信医务人员 一切交给他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们祈祷皇姐能尽快恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因也不要过于操心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的体贴和关怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Clydesdale队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全机展开！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang队长呼叫Mustang-00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈 部署得如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初步计算结果已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将坐标和时机发送给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-11&22 开始移动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ortygia的主体是最开始的那一架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同时攻击 摧毁主体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorraia小队 前行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gotland小队 从西边包抄过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorraia小队 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Gotland小队 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主体是右起第3台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们以为瞄准的是本体吗…不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人主力部队就由我这架Ortygia来接手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nonius小队 Pleven小队 集中攻击Skandia并将其击破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟幕弹 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射 发射 发射 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又用同样的手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一群无趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不这样想吗 泽布林伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来陪他们玩玩吧 拉菲亚伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胶体会被离子吸附
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.45,ruby,NTP,0,255,0,,Colloid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.45,ruby,NTP,100,0,0,,ion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是高压电的一种使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,透明机体放雷击了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢幕之际也要不失优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是真正的重甲骑兵驾驶员 应该会这么认为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主力部队和强袭部队好像都陷入了苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说雷击和透明在一起行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-00 情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据已经备齐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:10:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟幕的无效化和透明化的扩张倒是意料之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以弥补吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我倒下以后 战争已经持续了差不多2年时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这全都是斯雷因做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 您要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去见斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后去确认真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…你总是…抢走我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从战术数据链中将敌人的行动进行多次元解析
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而推测出驾驶员的攻击习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我方配置在容易受到对方的首选攻击的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱使敌人对他们进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 至于能否来得及解析就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将最新的数据发送给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙估计是个右撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了更容易攻击到左侧敌人 他会逆时针移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当诱饵真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方现在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正往你身后迂回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不泄露自己的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方停止了雷击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当对方到达敌人背后的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会暂时停下移动去瞄准敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪姐 趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Mustang队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mustang-00 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解 投下Mustang-00
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Skandia的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法承受Elektris的重量了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.72,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Got over it ages ago
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除合体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我 你快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.43,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Where we were from the same river
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认目标
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:34.31,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Thinking about how we lost our minds
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9号 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.56,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't care what's in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.69,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}They don't care about old trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说没用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.32,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Many wars wherever you go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝尝看我的炮弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.16,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Somebody please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.24,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can we stop all the fights?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:52.12,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do it because it's my turn
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电流是根据电势差而流动的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处在同一电势中的物体是不会受到闪电攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.08,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自身不会受到雷击也是同样道理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.25,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There are people crying everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.30,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's fly away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:06.26,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}For Earth and Mars today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经和你处在同一电势中了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.22,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't stop me now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:11.10,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:14.64,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}How can we stop the war
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是传说中的橙色恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.94,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Hello, But Are we sure enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽布林伯爵！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派增援过去 给我撑住！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:21.11,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll come back tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.24,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}But I need to know that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:26.03,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Look around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊奈帆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟幕弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.41,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So What are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.37,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Can I ask you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.79,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Why the sky is blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了！发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.29,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}There's no difference
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.42,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}You and me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 竟然将我的同志…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧 阿奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 雪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9点钟方向！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:07.52,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Coz It's time to wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:11.67,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Over there my friend now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.64,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Come on take my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！逐一攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.33,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Take it now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:18.11,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}See, Far away
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.26,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}See the dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:22.39,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}It's time to grow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.85,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Over there my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.43,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Here we are
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:31.24,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Come on! Just share this perfect sky
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:35.20,INEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}See the dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我吗 雷姆蕾娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.30,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主…皇姐已经…醒来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想过 此事最终还是要告诉您的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在可以向我说明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主还没有完全恢复记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在她恢复记忆之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要雷姆蕾娜公主继续扮演亚瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了创造新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一个无忧无虑的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有纷争 没有悲伤 幸福永久长存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁将会统治那个世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然是亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚公主殿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得皇姐渴望这种世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她不渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 这一切都由我来实现并奉献给她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下 您知道为什么会发生战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家之间的一种交涉手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 战争之所以会发生是因为有战斗对手的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要完全消除战争 只有两种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种是侵略对方将对方融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外一种就是将对方完全消灭只留下另外一方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的历史就是斗争的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自地球和火星分裂时起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争就已经无法避免了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就算我不去做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天也会有人去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不是我所熟知的那位斯雷因了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都和她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以巴斯第一皇女亚瑟拉姆·巴斯·艾莉欧西亚的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命斯雷因·扎赫巴姆·托罗亚特伯爵立即停战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是打倒主体就行了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪个才是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前标记的那台并不是主体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道躲在什么地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始以为它们其中一体会是主体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解析了分身之后 得出了很有意思的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙在出现的一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从姿势到能量状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都与主体保存着同样的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许对方是在使用量子传输创造自身的复制体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候 将复制品的原型保留下来 便形成了一个分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 什么意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将全重甲骑兵队的瞄准器和扳机交给我来控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向中队指挥提出请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入全Ortygia的坐标和向量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.39,ruby,NTP,420,0,0,,vector
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有多少个啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗 界冢弟弟！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标正在增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要一会才能更新完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个接一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹药不够撑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战术数据链同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全联合军的重甲骑兵瞄准集中控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿奈 还没好吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机会只有一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果全都是真的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全目标锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然全都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就在同一时间全部摧毁么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的重甲骑兵全被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 伊奈帆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 顺顺利利的真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了大家的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请结束这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟拉姆公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法听从您的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我已经不是巴斯帝国的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要限制你们的人身自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 总司令部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在激光通信卫星沉到水平线那头为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约有2分钟的通话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这点儿时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到扬声器上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Deucalion舰长达尔扎娜·马格巴丽吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是埃利斯·哈基宁中将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常精彩的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改造工作的进展情况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.48,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Deucalion执行新任务时所需的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往卫星带的任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的任务要前往更远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之后会将作战内容传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激光的增益下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信卫星的经度已经到达极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这话的意思就是没有选择吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来将会是一场大战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他觉得这艘船装备了Aldnoah Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以随便来使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙用的装备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹射器组件…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位公主已经回房安顿下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算她们现在不能理解斯雷因大人的苦心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是否能理解都无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯雷因大人 有飞船正在接近这个基地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们请求入港
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞船？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是来自巴斯母星的访问者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父亲长眠的蓝色之星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 库鲁迪欧伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样叫我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用父亲的名字称呼我还是挺不习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.09,0:21:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请叫我库朗凯因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就这样称呼您吧 库朗凯因伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我来会一会他吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托罗亚特博士的公子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.01,title,NTP,0,0,0,,“梦幻的彼方”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:32.87,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕たちは彷徨える未来　窮屈な空に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.57,0:22:32.87,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在彷徨的未来 在狭隘的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:37.21,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ヒカリを探している
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:37.21,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我们探寻光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:41.25,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}震える手は無力で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:41.25,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}颤抖着的双手是无力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.63,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}叫びはまだ遠くて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.63,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}呐喊又尚在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:53.06,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}だけど飛ぶことを　恐れではいられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:53.06,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}然而对于飞翔 绝不能感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:23:01.06,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}永遠じゃなくても　完璧じゃなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:23:01.06,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不永恒又何妨 不完美又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:08.49,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}背中合わせの世界を真っ直ぐ生きてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:08.49,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要在相互扶持的世界勇敢生存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.66,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何度傷ついても　何度間違えても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:15.66,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一次次的受伤算什么 一次次的错误算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.33,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}運命さえ飛び超えていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.33,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使是命运 我们也要一起飞越
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:24.96,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この宙の果てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:24.96,EDJP2,NTP,0,95,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\fs17}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:24.96,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}飞向宇宙的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:31.05,EDJP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}創造を信じで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:31.05,EDJP2,NTP,0,130,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)\fs17}はじまり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:31.05,EDCN2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}相信着创造的开始

